metadata.name: Divine Assembly Pre-Reveal
metadata.description: 7,890 3D designed characters elected by the Olympian gods. The Collection is divided into 4 main groups and combines more than 250 attributes. Divine Assembly is the 1st project dedicated to create a functional civilization inside the Metaverse. Being a holder will give you access to utilities in our eco-system that include : play-to-earn, vote, special airdrops, exclusive gifts and much more ! Electeds are stored as ERC-721 tokens on the Ethereum blockchain and hosted on IPFS.
